IMHO the main issue is that the logical flow jumps back and forth in the source code

mapping from the pipeline to the request at line 84
service definition (including the actual operation on the stub) at line 76
mapping the service response at line 85

And the complicated functions returning consumers/functions etc.. don't help:
FunctionEx<? super ManagedChannel, ? extends FunctionEx<StreamObserver<R>, StreamObserver<T>>>

